Our general members application has opened! 💡✨

We have 2 exciting projects for this year. As a general member, you will have a chance to contribute to brainstorming, research & decision making, hands-on prototyping, and building of these arcade games! 👾🕹️ 

Please refer to the AGM slides linked in the application form for more details on the projects! 🦖♟️

Please apply before Friday, September 20th at 11:59 pm EST through the link in our bio! ⚡️

Would you like to be a part of Spark’s Design Club to create fun and interactive displays across campus? Are you eager to develop practical engineering skills through hands-on experience? Did you enjoy interacting with our displays during F!rosh Week? 🦄💜

If you’ve answered ‘yes’ to any of these questions, we invite you to attend our Annual General Meeting next Thursday. Join us and discover everything about our design club! 🎮🕹️

📆 : Thursday, September 12th, 2024
⏰️ : 6-7 pm EST
🌐 : BA 2159 (and Zoom)

We will go over what Spark does in more detail, an overview of the two displays we have planned for this year, and how you can get involved. 🌱🌻

Sign up now through the link in our bio and read the description for more details. We hope to see you there! 👾🌟

Hey SLUGS! Have you or someone you know been looking to get more involved with SLUGS and join the exec team? If so, we are currently hosting a by-election for a new reading group coordinator! If you have any questions about the role or the election, please leave a comment or dm us!

Follow the link in our bio or scan the QR code for the nomination form! Nominations are open from NOW until Monday, September 30th at 11:59 pm!
